description:
Do you want Jesus to make a revival transformation in your life? Every thing starts with prayer when we ask through Him. Allow His Holy Spirit to teach you how to pray. Claim by faith and receive His gift.

Receive the the gift of Holy Spirit, that empowers us to receive all other gifts in God's storehouse. We are living on the edge of time. Let us all remain faithful through Christ. Continue to ask for the baptism of the Holy Spirit every day while waiting for Him. Let our lives be filled with the Holy Spirit of God.

Let us learn more about the power of the Holy Spirit. Listen to Dwight Nelson, a Seventh-day Adventist evangelist and author, as he speaks about the "Holy Spirit"  at the virtual global campmeeting sermon 7. Delight yourself as he gives you an idea why we need to ask of the Holy Spirit daily and let the  fruit of the Holy Spirit enable you to say, "iwillgo," in God's ministry.
